reviewText: Enjoyable and its George Clooney.  Need I say more?  Good price too.
I find INTOLERABLY CRUEL to be intolerably funny and creative, with plenty of surprises.

... gave both of these films my very best shot...... twice......  could not make it all the way through either film..... either time.... despite focused effort and resolve to get there.

Gave it yet a third attempt last evening...... and lost.....

Simply couldn't DO it!

Recycled the pair in garbage with warm relief in seeing these getting what they deserved....

Out of Sight/Intolerable Cruelty (Double Feature) with George Clooney;  are very good drama/suspense films for the price of one. Both movies have extras on them. Out of Sight has Jennifer Lopez with Clooney and it is a drama/comedy And Intolerable Cruelty is a Choen brother film. They are both rated R. I like them both and am glad to have them.

I hope you like them as I did.
I think this movie is one of George clooneys best acting roles,also jennifer lopez is great in this. It is a good story and very entertaining.
